"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2_Lore"       "一名传奇工匠制作了这件宝物的雏形，但一直苦于如何继续加工。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3"	"科伊的护心镜"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_Description"	"<h1>主动：阻止</h1> 以%abilitycastrange%范围内所有可见的敌方单位为目标，减缓其移动速度。<br>同时对自身施加弱驱散，提升移动速度，无法被减速，持续%purge_slow_duration%秒。<br><br>如果目标是非英雄，还会使其缠绕%purge_root_duration%秒。<br><br>移动速度减缓和提升效果在状态持续时间内初始均为100%%，并且逐渐减少至0。\n\n<h1>被动：破法</h1>每次攻击将燃烧目标%feedback_mana_burn%点魔法，而且每燃烧一点魔法都会造成%damage_per_burn%点物理伤害。\n<h1>被动：战场急救</h1>对中立生物造成攻击伤害后获得护盾，护盾可以吸收来自中立生物的物理伤害，数值相当于攻击伤害的%shield_hp_pct%%%，每次最多%max_shield_hp%点，持续%shield_duration%秒。<br><br>护盾最大叠加数值为%max_hp_base% + %max_hp_pct%%%施法者最大生命值。\n<h1>被动：战术专家</h1>攻击有%buff_chance%%%几率获得增益效果，使你受到的来自中立生物的伤害降低%creep_damage_reduce%%%，持续%buff_duration%秒。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_Lore"   "名叫科伊的战士带来一块珍贵的石材；两个月后，护心镜终于完成。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_slow"		"阻止"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_slow_Description"	"移动速度降低%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_root"		"阻止"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_root_Description"	"被缠绕"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_buff"	"被散魂"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_buff_Description"	"无法被减速。移动速度提升%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff"	"NH老师的魔杖"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff_manacost_reduction"	"%+$manacost_reduction"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff_Description"	"<h1>被动：奥术超载</h1>魔法伤害有%magic_crit_pct%%%概率造成%magic_crit_damage%%%伤害。<br><br>百分比类技能无效"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>“ 一根传承着远古法术能量的魔杖 ”</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen"	"堕落者之颅"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_all_stats"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_bonus_hp_regen"	"+$hp_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Description"	"<h1>主动：军团降临</h1>邪能统御光环提供技能免疫和克敌机先，持续%duration%秒。<br><br>无法被刷新\n<h1>被动：邪能统御</h1>为周围友军提供%life_steal_pct%%%吸血，%bonus_movespeed%移动速度，%bonus_attack_speed%攻击速度，%spell_amp%%%技能增强，%magical_resistance%%%魔法抗性和%evasion%%%闪避，同时让邪能火焰包围友军，每%burn_interval%秒对友军%burn_radius%范围内的敌人造成%burn_damage%点魔法伤害，邪能火焰可以叠加。<br><br>对非英雄友军产生%creep_mult%%%的效果。<br><br>作用范围：%radius%"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>“ 我们响应了召唤，但代价是什么呢？ ”</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_effect"		"邪能统御"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_effect_Description"	"获得%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%吸血，移动速度提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%，攻击速度提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%，技能增强提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_SPELL_AMPLIFY_PERCENTAGE%%%，魔法抗性提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MAGICAL_RESISTANCE_BONUS%%%，闪避提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_EVASION_CONSTANT%%%，不断灼烧周围的敌人。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Active"		"军团降临"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Active_Description"	"邪能统御光环提供技能免疫和克敌机先效果"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_burn"		"邪能火焰"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_burn_Description"	"你的灵魂将受到折磨！"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff"	"观星者"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_manacost_reduction"	"%+$manacost_reduction"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_all_stats"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_Description"	"<h1>主动：魔法虚弱</h1>发出一波弱化冲击，使%debuff_radius%范围内敌人受到的魔法伤害增加%bonus_magical_dmg%%%。<br><br>施法距离：%abilitycastrange%<br>持续时间：%debuff_duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：棱光屏障</h1>每当你的魔法伤害暴击，使你获得增益效果，使你受到的来自中立生物的伤害降低%creep_damage_reduce%%%，持续%buff_duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：奥术涌动</h1>魔法伤害有%magic_crit_pct%%%概率造成%magic_crit_damage%%%伤害。<br><br>冷却时间：%crit_cd%秒，可以受到冷却时间减少效果影响，对受到魔法虚弱影响的中立生物没有冷却时间。<br><br>百分比类技能无效"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_Lore"	"一把由陨星铸成的法杖"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_cd"		"奥术涌动"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_cd_Description"	"奥术涌动处在冷却中"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_buff"		"棱光屏障"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_buff_Description"	"来自中立生物的伤害降低%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_INCOMING_DAMAGE_PERCENTAGE%%%"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_debuff"	"魔法虚弱"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_debuff_Description"	"受到的魔法伤害提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>加思特，护法者之杖</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_manacost_reduction"	"%+$manacost_reduction"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_Description"	"<h1>主动：魔法虚弱</h1>发出一波弱化冲击，将%debuff_radius%范围内敌人缠绕，持续%root_duration%秒，并使其受到的魔法伤害增加%bonus_magical_dmg%%%，持续%debuff_duration%秒。<br><br>如果目标是非英雄，还会使其暂时失去所有魔法值，这些魔法值在缠绕效果结束后恢复。<br><br>施法距离：%abilitycastrange%\n<h1>被动：棱光屏障</h1>每当你的魔法伤害暴击，使你获得增益效果，使你受到的来自中立生物的伤害降低%creep_damage_reduce%%%，持续%buff_duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：奥术涌动</h1>魔法伤害有%magic_crit_pct%%%概率造成%magic_crit_damage%%%伤害。<br><br>冷却时间：%crit_cd%秒<br><br>对受到魔法虚弱影响的中立生物没有冷却时间，并且触发概率提高%bonus_magic_cirt_pct%%%。<br><br>百分比类技能无效"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>“ 为了维护秘法议会的至高权益，数名最强大的护法者向这把法杖中注入了几乎所有力量 ”</font>"
