"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_reroll_token_lua_tier4"	"第4级重铸代币"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_reroll_token_lua_tier4_Description"	"<h1>使用：重铸</h1>从%choice%件新的第%tier%级中立物品中选择一件，替换当前的第%tier%级中立物品。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_reroll_token_lua_tier5"	"第5级重铸代币"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_reroll_token_lua_tier5_Description"	"<h1>使用：重铸</h1>从%choice%件新的第%tier%级中立物品中选择一件，替换当前的第%tier%级中立物品。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon"	"<font color='#ff8000'>月神殿长弓</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_bonus_attack_range"	"+$attack_range"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_projectile_speed"	"+$projectile_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_Description"	"<h1>被动：月光大箭</h1>每次攻击都会射出%arrow_count%支月光箭。月光箭造成%arrow_dmg_pct%%%攻击力的魔法伤害，敌人越远，伤害越高，并将其推开至最远%max_knockback_distance%距离。<br><br>不会将敌人击退到你的攻击距离之外。<br><br>距离伤害加成：%arrow_bonus_dmg_per_range%%%。\n<h1>被动：神射手的专注</h1>远程英雄装备时，每1点主属性提供%bonus_range_per_stat%攻击距离。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>“ 月亮井的能量流遍弓身 ”</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller"	"<font color='#ff8000'>风神的唤雷剑</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_Description"	"<h1>被动：舞跃之雷</h1>攻击击中敌人时释放一道跳跃的闪电，打击%jump_count%名敌人，闪电的伤害为攻击伤害的%damage_pct%%%，被闪电击中的敌人会进入<font color='#69b7f2'>通电</font>状态，持续%slow_duration%秒。<br><br><font color='#69b7f2'>通电</font>状态下的敌人受到的物理伤害提高%bonus_damage_pct%%%，攻击速度降低%attack_slow%，施法速度降低%cast_slow%%%，并且无法获得克敌机先。\n<h1>被动：雷暴</h1>普通攻击和舞跃之雷有%crit_chance%%%几率造成%crit_damage%%%伤害。\n<h1>被动：风驰电掣</h1>移动速度提高%bonus_movespeed%%%。近战英雄装备时，提高%bonus_attack_speed_pct%%%攻击速度。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>“ 觉醒吧，雷霆之怒！ ”</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_thunder_caller_debuff"	"<font color='#69b7f2'>通电</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_thunder_caller_debuff_Description"	"受到的物理伤害提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_INCOMING_PHYSICAL_DAMAGE_PERCENTAGE%%%，攻击速度降低%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%，施法速度降低%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_CASTTIME_PERCENTAGE%%%，并且无法获得克敌机先。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul"	"<font color='#ff8000'>瑞兹的寄魂杖</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_Description"	"<h1>主动：无限火力</h1>在%duration%秒内尽情施法，期间你免疫沉默，并使你技能和物品的施法前摇降低%casttime_reduction%%%，魔法消耗提高%bonus_manacost%%%，施法距离提高%bonus_cast_range%，冷却时间降低%cooldown_reduction%%%，但不低于%cooldown_min%秒。<br><br>不能被刷新。<br>不能减少刷新球的冷却时间。\n<h1>被动：奥术专精</h1>提供魔法恢复增强，这个效果随着你的魔法值降低而大幅增强。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>“ 这名强大的符文法师最终选择这柄法杖作为他灵魂的归宿 ”</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_ryze_soul_buff"	"无限火力"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_ryze_soul_buff_Description"	"狂轰滥炸！"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_moon_shard"		"暗月之晶"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_moon_shard_Description"	"<h1>使用：吞噬</h1>吞噬暗月之晶，永久降低%base_attack_time_reduction%% 基础攻击间隔，但不低于%base_attack_time_min%。 最多使用一次。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_moon_shard_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_moon_shard"	"暗月之晶"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_moon_shard_Description"	"基础攻击间隔降低至%fMODIFIER_PROPERTY_BASE_ATTACK_TIME_CONSTANT%"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song"	"<font color='#c600ff'>碧空之歌</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_health"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_spell_amp"	"%+$spell_amp"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_mana_regen_multiplier"	"%+魔法恢复增强"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_spell_lifesteal_amp"	"%+技能吸血增强"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_Description"	"<h1>被动：法术强化</h1>你的下次技能或物品伤害会额外对目标及其%radius%范围内的敌人造成%bonus_dmg%点魔法伤害，并且减速%movement_slow%%%，持续%slow_duration%秒。<br><br>被动技能不会触发这个效果。\n<h1>被动：香芒之力！</h1>每1智力提高%spell_amp_per_int%%%技能伤害，每1力量/敏捷提高%spell_amp_per_other%%%技能伤害。<br><br>以英雄为目标时仅有%hero_pct%%%的效果。<br><br>百分比类技能无效。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_Lore"	"一柄洋溢着魔法能量的长剑，在那个年代是无数法师的追求"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song_slow"	"法术强化"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song_slow_Description"	"移动速度减缓%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>星斗宏图</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song_Description"	"<font color='#B694FF'>总技能增强</font>提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>星斗宏图</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_health"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_spell_amp"	"%+$spell_amp"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_mana_regen_multiplier"	"%+魔法恢复增强"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_spell_lifesteal_amp"	"%+技能吸血增强"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_Description"	"<h1>被动：法术强化</h1>你的下次技能或物品伤害会额外对目标及其%radius%范围内的敌人造成%bonus_dmg%点魔法伤害，并且减速%movement_slow%%%，持续%slow_duration%秒。<br><br>被动技能不会触发这个效果。\n<h1>被动：香芒之力！</h1>每1智力提高%spell_amp_per_int%%%技能伤害，每1力量/敏捷提高%spell_amp_per_other%%%技能伤害。<br><br>以英雄为目标时仅有%hero_pct%%%的效果。<br><br>百分比类技能无效。\n<h1>被动：星穹铁帽</h1>在白天，这件物品每有%total_spell_amp_threshold%点能量，就使你的<font color='#B694FF'>总技能增强</font>提高%total_spell_amp_pct_day%%%。<br><br>在晚上，这件物品每有%total_spell_amp_threshold%点能量，就使你的<font color='#B694FF'>总技能增强</font>提高%total_spell_amp_pct_night%%%。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_Lore"	"<font color='#B694FF'>天上天下，唯法独尊。</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker"	"风味奥术鞋"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_mana_pct"	"%+$max_mana_percentage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_movement"	"+$move_speed"
// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_mana_regen_multiplier"	"%+魔法恢复增强"
// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_spell_lifesteal_amp"	"%+技能吸血增强"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_Description"	"<h1>主动：补魔</h1>回复英雄%replenish_amount%点魔法。<br><br>每失去%one_pct_tooltip%%%的魔法，魔法的回复量提高%bonus_replenish_amount_pct%%%。\n<h1>被动：以太焦点</h1>提升%cast_range_bonus%指向性技能和物品的施法距离。\n<h1>被动：魔法贯刺</h1>提供%magical_armor_pen%%%<font color='#B694FF'>法术穿透</font>。<br><br>初始拥有%initial_charge%点能量。<br>每击杀一名敌方英雄，你获得%kill_charge%点能量，最多获得%max_charge%点能量。<br>每%one_pct_tooltip%点能量提供%magical_armor_pen_pct_charge%%%<font color='#B694FF'>百分比法术穿透</font>，对抗英雄时还会提供%spell_amp_charge%%%技能伤害。<br>当你被敌方英雄杀死时，你失去%death_lose_charge%点能量。<br><br>百分比类技能无效。\n多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_Lore"	"因为是法师穿的鞋子，所以你也可以叫它：法穿鞋"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_arcane_walker_magical_armor_pen"	"法术穿透"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_arcane_walker_magical_armor_pen_Description"	"被视为仅有%fMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%魔法抗性"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter"	"假腿帮信函"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_str"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_Description"	"<h1>被动：势力光环</h1>强化你控制的非英雄单位，使他们获得：<br>每1属性增加%aura_bonus_damage_str%%%基础攻击力<br>每1力量增加%aura_bonus_hp_str%%%最大生命值，对攻击者造成%aura_bonus_return_str%物理伤害。<br>每1敏捷增加%aura_bonus_armor_agi%护甲和%aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi%攻击速度<br>攻击额外造成%aura_bonus_magical_damage_int%魔法伤害，每1智力增加%aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%%技能伤害和%aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%魔法抗性<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。如果同时装备多份信函，仅有最后一份会生效。\n这件物品视为一件鞋类物品，多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_letter_effect"	"势力光环"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_letter_effect_Description"	"攻击力提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_BASEDAMAGEOUTGOING_PERCENTAGE%%%，生命值提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_EXTRA_HEALTH_PERCENTAGE%%%，攻击速度提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%，护甲提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS%，技能伤害提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_SPELL_AMPLIFY_PERCENTAGE%%%，魔法抗性提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MAGICAL_RESISTANCE_BONUS%%%。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter"	"假腿帮高层信函"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_str"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_Description"	"<h1>被动：势力光环</h1>强化你控制的非英雄单位，使他们获得：<br>每1属性增加%aura_bonus_damage_str%%%基础攻击力<br>每1力量增加%aura_bonus_hp_str%%%最大生命值，对攻击者造成%aura_bonus_return_str%物理伤害。（%aura_bonus_return_str_cd%秒冷却时间）<br>每1敏捷增加%aura_bonus_armor_agi%护甲和%aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi%攻击速度<br>攻击额外造成%aura_bonus_magical_damage_int%魔法伤害，每1智力增加%aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%%技能伤害和%aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%魔法抗性<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。如果同时装备多份信函，仅有最后一份会生效。\n这件物品视为一件鞋类物品，多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter"	"假腿帮鬼故事"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_spell_amp"	"%+$spell_amp"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_Description"	"<h1>主动：鞋灵猎杀</h1>使正处于势力光环作用下的友军获得克敌机先，但攻击的伤害类型不会改变，持续%duration%秒。<br><br>可以攻击虚无状态下的单位，额外造成%damage_pct%%%攻击力的魔法伤害。<br><br>以及：<br>将施法者的%bonus_spell_amp_active%%%技能增强共享给他们<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n<h1>被动：势力光环</h1>强化你控制的非英雄单位，使他们获得：<br>每1属性增加%aura_bonus_damage_str%%%基础攻击力<br>每1力量增加%aura_bonus_hp_str%%%最大生命值，对攻击者造成%aura_bonus_return_str%物理伤害。（%aura_bonus_return_str_cd%秒冷却时间）<br>每1敏捷增加%aura_bonus_armor_agi%护甲和%aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi%攻击速度<br>攻击额外造成%aura_bonus_magical_damage_int%魔法伤害，每1智力增加%aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%%技能伤害和%aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%魔法抗性<br><br>以及：<br>+%aura_spell_amp_constant%%%技能伤害<br>+%aura_projectile_speed%弹道速度<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。如果同时装备多份信函，仅有最后一份会生效。\n这件物品视为一件鞋类物品，多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_ghost_letter"	"鞋灵猎杀"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_ghost_letter_Description"	"获得克敌机先，可以攻击虚无状态下的单位。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter"	"假腿帮餐券"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_hp_regen_pct"	"%+最大生命恢复"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_Description"	"<h1>被动：吃吧！</h1>将你所受伤害的%link_damage%%%转嫁到一个势力光环作用下的友军身上，优先选择生命值最高的单位。\n<h1>被动：势力光环</h1>强化你控制的非英雄单位，使他们获得：<br>每1属性增加%aura_bonus_damage_str%%%基础攻击力<br>每1力量增加%aura_bonus_hp_str%%%最大生命值，被攻击时对攻击者造成%aura_bonus_return_str%物理伤害（%aura_bonus_return_str_cd%秒冷却时间）<br>每1敏捷增加%aura_bonus_armor_agi%护甲和%aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi%攻击速度<br>攻击额外造成%aura_bonus_magical_damage_int%魔法伤害，每1智力增加%aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%%技能伤害和%aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%魔法抗性<br><br>以及：<br>+%aura_hp_regen_pct%%%最大生命恢复<br>+%aura_lifesteal%%%共有吸血（对守卫效果降低%aura_lifesteal_other%%%）<br>+%aura_bonus_damage_pct%%%攻击力加成<br>+%aura_bonus_armor%护甲<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。如果同时装备多份信函，仅有最后一份会生效。\n这件物品视为一件鞋类物品，多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet"	"假腿帮战书"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_Description"	"<h1>被动：街头火并</h1>势力光环作用下的友军每次攻击均有%aura_accuracy_chance%%%概率无视闪避，并有%aura_bash_chance%%%的概率击晕目标%aura_bash_duration%秒。以中立生物为目标时无冷却。\n<h1>被动：势力光环</h1>强化你控制的非英雄单位，使他们获得：<br>每1属性增加%aura_bonus_damage_str%%%基础攻击力<br>每1力量增加%aura_bonus_hp_str%%%最大生命值，被攻击时对攻击者造成%aura_bonus_return_str%物理伤害（%aura_bonus_return_str_cd%秒冷却时间）<br>每1敏捷增加%aura_bonus_armor_agi%护甲和%aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi%攻击速度<br>攻击额外造成%aura_bonus_magical_damage_int%魔法伤害，每1智力增加%aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%%技能伤害和%aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%魔法抗性<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。如果同时装备多份信函，仅有最后一份会生效。\n这件物品视为一件鞋类物品，多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket"	"假腿帮机票"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_Description"	"<h1>主动：伞兵空降</h1>将势力光环作用下的友军传送到最远%abilitycastrange%的位置，并使敌人恐惧%duration%秒。<br><br>作用范围：%blink_radius%\n<h1>被动：势力光环</h1>强化你控制的非英雄单位，使他们获得：<br>每1属性增加%aura_bonus_damage_str%%%基础攻击力<br>每1力量增加%aura_bonus_hp_str%%%最大生命值，被攻击时对攻击者造成%aura_bonus_return_str%物理伤害（%aura_bonus_return_str_cd%秒冷却时间）<br>每1敏捷增加%aura_bonus_armor_agi%护甲和%aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi%攻击速度<br>攻击额外造成%aura_bonus_magical_damage_int%魔法伤害，每1智力增加%aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%%技能伤害和%aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%魔法抗性<br><br>以及：<br>+%aura_attack_range%攻击距离<font color='#7d7d7d'>（仅对远程有效）</font><br>+%aura_attack_range_melee%攻击距离<font color='#7d7d7d'>（仅对近战有效）</font><br>每次攻击时有%aura_crit_chance%%%概率造成%aura_crit_damage%%%伤害<br>如果攻击一名被恐惧的敌人，必定造成%aura_crit_damage%%%伤害<br><br>作用范围：%aura_radius%\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。如果同时装备多份信函，仅有最后一份会生效。\n这件物品视为一件鞋类物品，多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_plane_ticket"	"逮个正着"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_plane_ticket_Description"	"快逃！"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots"	"血精鞋"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_mana_pct"	"%+$max_mana_percentage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_movement"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_spell_lifesteal"	"%+$spell_lifesteal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_Description"	"<h1>主动：血精契约</h1>回复英雄%replenish_amount%点魔法。<br><br>每失去%one_pct_tooltip%%%的魔法，魔法的回复量提高%bonus_replenish_amount_pct%%%。<br><br>血精鞋的技能吸血效果提高%lifesteal_multiplier%倍，并且造成伤害的相同百分比转化为魔法，持续%duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：以太焦点</h1>提升%cast_range_bonus%指向性技能和物品的施法距离。\n<h1>被动：魔法贯刺</h1>提供%magical_armor_pen%%%<font color='#B694FF'>法术穿透</font>。<br><br>初始拥有%initial_charge%点能量。<br>每击杀一名敌方英雄，你获得%kill_charge%点能量，最多获得%max_charge%点能量。<br>每%one_pct_tooltip%点能量提供%magical_armor_pen_pct_charge%%%<font color='#B694FF'>百分比法术穿透</font>和%spell_lifesteal_charge%%%技能吸血，对抗英雄时还会提供%spell_amp_charge%%%技能伤害。<br>当你被敌方英雄杀死时，你失去%death_lose_charge%点能量。<br><br>百分比类技能无效。\n多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_Lore"	"海克斯科技制造。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_blood_boots"	"血精契约"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_blood_boots_Description"	"血精鞋的技能吸血效果提高。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh"	"<font color='#c600ff'>最后的笑容</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_health_regen"   "+$hp_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_mana_regen"   "+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_attack_range"	"+$attack_range"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_attack_range_melee"	"+$attack_range_melee"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Description"	"<h1>主动：相位移动</h1>提升%phase_movement_speed_pct%%%移动速度并使你可以穿越单位和树木，转身也更快，持续%duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：压制</h1>总攻击力提高%quelling_bonus%%%。<br><br>攻击非中立生物会使这个效果减弱%hero_pct_reduction%%%，持续%disable_duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：分裂</h1>近战/远程英雄普通攻击时对目标周围最远%cleave_distance%/%cleave_distance_ranged%距离的锥形区域内敌人造成%cleave_damage_percent%%%/%cleave_damage_percent_ranged%%%物理伤害。\n多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Note0"	"分裂伤害无视减益免疫。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Note1"	"如果存在多个分裂效果，每个分裂的伤害都会单独计算。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh"	"致命一击"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_Description"	"致命一击触发几率提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%，伤害提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP2%%%。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_active"	"相位移动"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_active_Description"	"移动速度提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%，可以穿越单位和树木。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_disable"	"放你一马"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Lore"	"握着这把强大的斧头可以一次砍倒一片敌人。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>火之高高兴</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_health_regen"   "+$hp_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_mana_regen"   "+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_attack_range"	"+$attack_range"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_attack_range_melee"	"+$attack_range_melee"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Description"	"<h1>主动：相位移动</h1>提升%phase_movement_speed_pct%%%移动速度并使你可以穿越单位和树木，转身也更快，持续%duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：压制</h1>总攻击力提高%quelling_bonus%%%。<br><br>攻击非中立生物会使这个效果减弱%hero_pct_reduction%%%，持续%disable_duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：分裂</h1>近战/远程英雄普通攻击时对目标周围最远%cleave_distance%/%cleave_distance_ranged%距离的锥形区域内敌人造成%cleave_damage_percent%%%/%cleave_damage_percent_ranged%%%物理伤害。\n<h1>被动：致命一击</h1>普通攻击有%crit_chance%%%几率造成%crit_multiplier%%%伤害。\n多个鞋类物品提供的移动速度加成不叠加。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Note0"	"分裂伤害无视减益免疫。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Note1"	"如果存在多个分裂效果，每个分裂的伤害都会单独计算。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Lore"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>一刀足矣。</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor"	"云割"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor_Description"	"<h1>被动：切割</h1>物理伤害将降低目标%corruption_armor%护甲，持续%corruption_duration%秒。<br><br>初始拥有%initial_charge%点能量。<br>每击杀一名敌方英雄，你获得%kill_charge%点能量，最多获得%max_charge%点能量。<br>每%one_pct_tooltip%点能量将额外降低目标%corruption_armor_pct_charge%%%护甲。<br>当你被敌方英雄杀死时，你失去%death_lose_charge%点能量。\n<h1>被动：穿刺</h1>每次攻击都具有克敌机先，并造成额外%bonus_chance_damage%点魔法伤害。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_cloud_razor_corruption"	"切割"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_cloud_razor_corruption_Description"	"护甲降低%fMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS%点。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blade_mail_Lore"		"<font color='#ffffff'>这是一个<font color='#e80000'>反击法术</font>。</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thanksgiving_turkey"	"感恩节火鸡"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thanksgiving_turkey_Description"	"<h1>主动：大吃一鸡</h1>享用火鸡，将你的英雄提升至%UptoLevel%级。\n这只火鸡简直香疯了，你已经等不及要吃了。<br>最好在升到%UptoLevel%级前吃。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_surprise_gift"	"圣旦好礼"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_surprise_gift_Description"	"<h1>主动：拆开礼物</h1>拆开你的礼物，得到一份随机的惊喜！"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_revenants_brooch_Lore"		"<font color='#ffffff'><font color='#00BFFF'>碧空之歌</font>和<font color='#00BFFF'>星斗宏图</font>不能提高该技能的伤害。</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield"	"黯淡之盾"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield_Description"	"<h1>被动：弃明投暗</h1>装备的英雄每受到%stack_threshold%点减免前的物理伤害，就会获得一层持续%stack_duration%秒的叠加效果，最多为%max_stacks%层。每层效果会使这件物品的护甲提高%stack_armor%点。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_shield_stack"	"弃明投暗"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_shield_stack_Description"	"护甲提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%点。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power"	"荒邪之力"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_strength"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_lifesteal_percent"	"%+$lifesteal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_Description"	"<h1>主动：不洁狂热</h1>吸血效果提升至%unholy_lifesteal_percent%%%，持续%unholy_duration%秒。<br><br>驱散类型：<span class=\"GameplayValues GameplayVariable\">弱驱散</span> \n<h1>被动：吸血</h1>攻击者每次攻击都将根据造成伤害的一定百分比回复生命值。攻击非英雄单位的吸血效果降低%creep_lifesteal_reduction_pct%%%。\n<h1>被动：暗影墙</h1>这件物品产生超量治疗的%heal_to_shield%%%会转化为全伤害护盾，持续%shield_duration%秒，护盾最大叠加数值为%max_shield%。\n<h1>被动：弃明投暗</h1>装备的英雄每受到%stack_threshold%点减免前的物理伤害，就会获得一层持续%stack_duration%秒的叠加效果，最多为%max_stacks%层。每层效果会使这件物品的护甲提高%stack_armor%点。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。\n荒邪之力和血色残阳不能同时生效。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power_shield"	"暗影墙"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power_shield_Description"	"吸收伤害。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power"				"不洁狂热"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power_Description"			"吸血增加。"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3"	"血色残阳"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_aoe"	"+$aoe_bonus"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_health"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_spell_lifesteal"	"%+$spell_lifesteal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_Description"    "<h1>主动：血之契约</h1>这件物品的技能吸血效果提升至%lifesteal_multiplier%倍，并且回复等同于治疗量的魔法值。持续%buff_duration%秒。\n<h1>被动：血色护盾</h1>这件物品产生超量治疗的%heal_to_shield%%%会转化为全伤害护盾，持续%shield_duration%秒，护盾最大叠加数值为%max_shield%。\n<h1>被动：弃明投暗</h1>装备的英雄每受到%stack_threshold%点减免前的物理伤害，就会获得一层持续%stack_duration%秒的叠加效果，最多为%max_stacks%层。每层效果会使这件物品的护甲提高%stack_armor%点。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。\n荒邪之力和血色残阳不能同时生效。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_shield"	"血色护盾"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_shield_Description"	"吸收伤害。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3"	"血之契约"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_Description"	"技能吸血增加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_drained"	"精疲力竭"
