"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2"	"苍闪"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_Description"	"<h1>被动：疾风迅意</h1>攻击速度提升%bonus_attack_speed_pct%%%，敏捷提升%bonus_agi_pct%%%。<br><br>装备的英雄每有%bonus_attack_speed_limit_threshold%敏捷，最大攻击速度提升%bonus_attack_speed_limit%，最多提升%bonus_attack_speed_limit_max%。\n<h1>被动：振翅</h1>每次攻击命中会提供%buff_attack_speed%攻击速度，持续%buff_duration%秒，至多可叠加%buff_max_stack%次。在满层状态下，额外提供%buff_attack_speed_max_stack%攻击速度和%buff_agi_max_stack%敏捷。\n这件物品是唯一的，它的所有属性与效果不可叠加。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2"	"疾风迅意"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2_Description"	"最大攻击速度提高%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%（最大%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP2%）。"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2_buff_damage"	"振翅"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2_buff_damage_Description"	"攻击速度提升%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%，敏捷提升%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_STATS_AGILITY_BONUS%。"

